narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: A general mathematical understanding of how most data mining concepts work, many of which are the building blocks of modern machine learning techniques.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments: I liked how the course explained these concepts through proofs rather than just explaining the results. I wish the proofs were written on the board step by step rather than projected on powerpoint.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: If you want to work in this area of computer science than definitely yes, you definitely need to have your own initiative to learn the material fully.
